@node Main "Cellz - Documentation"

                              'Cellz'  1.07

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Cellz' is a 2 player strategy @{" game " link play}. The goal is to get a
certain number of cells before the opposing player does. The game is
based in part on the cellular reproduction (hence it's name), but it
is completely random.

  There are many game strategies which the players can use in order
the get some advantages (i.e. more cells), so the player who has the
best strategies (and luck) will win...

  You can choose the total number of cells to reach for (between 10 and
150 cells, by a step of 5 cells), when you have choosen a number, click
on the 'Play!' button to play the game.

  Have fun!

